name: Free Safari
description:
Free Safari is great... when you are a Zebra?!

Use the spacebar to jump and avoid the rocks, bushes, cars, and bullets that might get in your way!

Runner with health points which not help you with bullets and cars hitting you.

Welcome to our promo action: the most amazing safari in your life - is free for everyone. And - the new angle of view!

Trijam #202 submission. Made by team of 3. 

Programmer:  https://bohdan-zoshchenko.itch.io/
